<html>
<body>
Reports any include directives in a JSP file which refer to the containing JSP file.<br/>

<p><b>Example JSP file named main.jsp:</b></p>
<pre><code>
  &lt;jsp:include page="./main.jsp" /&gt; // Error: attempt to include the containing file
  ...
</code></pre><br/>

<!-- tooltip end -->
<p>
  <b>NOTE:</b> Such self-including leads to infinite recursion and so the JSP file cannot be compiled.
</p>
</body>
</html>

